thread.title: Uber, Waymo settle ugly dispute over self-driving tech

title: Uber, Waymo settle ugly dispute over self-driving tech
text:
Uber, Waymo settle ugly dispute over self-driving tech 7:40pm GMT - 01:41 
The self-driving car trial between Uber and Google car company Waymo came to a sudden halt on Friday as the two sides settled a trade secret case. But not before Waymo got to drag Uber through the mud.
